-- MOVES-Amlin names Louis de Segonzac head of reinsurance office at Miami
-- By Rama Venkat Raman in Bangalore
-- Mon Oct 13, 2014 03:39AM EDT
-- None



Oct 13 (Reuters) - British insurer Amlin Plc <AML.L> said it appointed Louis de Segonzac to lead underwriting activities at its Miami office.

Segonzac previously worked as a broker at Jardine Lloyd Thompson Group Plc <JLT.L>.